Some of the best Caribbean food I’ve ever eaten!! Super yummy. At least pre-Covid, they were always busy with tons of regulars and I think this says a lot in a neighborhood of predominantly Caribbean immigrants. Friendly staff. Great jerk chicken! Make sure to get everything covered in oxtail gravy! Come earlier in the day since by the end of the day the chicken isn’t as moist as it is earlier on. Would recommend any time of day though honestly! They really put a lot of pride and care into their food!
